structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.text: The provisions of KRS 65.8801 to 65.8839 may be cited as the "Local Government Code Enforcement Board Act."
law.history: Created 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 177, sec. 13, effective July 15, 1996.
